name: Picker Detail Report
query:
select pl.picker as "Picker::200",pli.sales_order as "Sales Order::160",soi.item_code as "Item Code::250",pl.start_time
     ,pl.end_time ,
    timediff(pl.end_time,pl.start_time) as "Lama Waktu Pengerjaan:200",soi.qty as "Quantity:Float:90" from `tabPick List` pl inner join `tabPick List Item` pli on pl.name = pli.parent
    inner join `tabSales Order Item` soi on pli.sales_order = soi.parent
    where pl.picker is not null and pli.sales_order is not null;
